{"tha-ap332:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap332:0.2":"Umapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap332:0.3":"Saparivarachattadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap332:1.1":"“Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap332:1.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap332:1.3":"Akase jalavutthiva, ","tha-ap332:1.4":"vassate dhammavutthiya. ","tha-ap332:2.1":"Tamaddasasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap332:2.2":"desentam amatam padam; ","tha-ap332:2.3":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap332:2.4":"agamasim sakam gharam. ","tha-ap332:3.1":"Chattam alankatam gayha, ","tha-ap332:3.2":"upagacchim naruttamam; ","tha-ap332:3.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap332:3.4":"akase ukkhipim aham. ","tha-ap332:4.1":"Susangahitayanamva, ","tha-ap332:4.2":"dantova savakuttamo; ","tha-ap332:4.3":"Upagantvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap332:4.4":"matthake sampatitthahi. ","tha-ap332:5.1":"Anukampako karuniko, ","tha-ap332:5.2":"buddho lokagganayako; ","tha-ap332:5.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap332:5.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap332:6.1":"‘Yena chattamidam dinnam, ","tha-ap332:6.2":"alankatam manoramam; ","tha-ap332:6.3":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap332:6.4":"duggatim so na gacchati. ","tha-ap332:7.1":"Sattakkhattunca devesu, ","tha-ap332:7.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap332:7.3":"Battimsakkhattunca raja, ","tha-ap332:7.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap332:8.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap332:8.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap332:8.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap332:8.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap332:9.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap332:9.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap332:9.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap332:9.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap332:10.1":"Buddhassa giramannaya, ","tha-ap332:10.2":"vacasabhimudiritam; ","tha-ap332:10.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap332:10.4":"bhiyyo hasam janesaham. ","tha-ap332:11.1":"Jahitva manusam yonim, ","tha-ap332:11.2":"Dibbam yonim samajjhagam; ","tha-ap332:11.3":"Vimanamuttamam mayham, ","tha-ap332:11.4":"Abbhuggatam manoramam. ","tha-ap332:12.1":"Vimana nikkhamantassa, ","tha-ap332:12.2":"setacchattam dhariyati; ","tha-ap332:12.3":"Tada sannam patilabhim, ","tha-ap332:12.4":"pubbakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap332:13.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap332:13.2":"manussattanca agamim; ","tha-ap332:13.3":"Chattimsakkhattum cakkavatti, ","tha-ap332:13.4":"sattakappasatamhito. ","tha-ap332:14.1":"Tamha kaya cavitvana, ","tha-ap332:14.2":"agacchim tidasam puram; ","tha-ap332:14.3":"Samsaritvanupubbena, ","tha-ap332:14.4":"manusam punaragamim. ","tha-ap332:15.1":"Okkantam matukucchim mam, ","tha-ap332:15.2":"setacchattam adharayum; ","tha-ap332:15.3":"Jatiya sattavassoham, ","tha-ap332:15.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap332:16.1":"Sunando nama namena, ","tha-ap332:16.2":"brahmano mantaparagu; ","tha-ap332:16.3":"Phalikam chattamadaya, ","tha-ap332:16.4":"savakaggassa so tada. ","tha-ap332:17.1":"Anumodi mahaviro, ","tha-ap332:17.2":"sariputto mahakathi; ","tha-ap332:17.3":"Sutvanumodanam tassa, ","tha-ap332:17.4":"pubbakammamanussarim. ","tha-ap332:18.1":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap332:18.2":"sakam cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap332:18.3":"Saritva purimam kammam, ","tha-ap332:18.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap332:19.1":"Utthaya asana tamha, ","tha-ap332:19.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap332:19.3":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap332:19.4":"imam vacam udirayim. ","tha-ap332:20.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap332:20.2":"buddho loke anuttaro; ","tha-ap332:20.3":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap332:20.4":"ahutinam patiggaho. ","tha-ap332:21.1":"Tassa chattam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap332:21.2":"vicittam samalankatam; ","tha-ap332:21.3":"Ubho hatthehi pagganhi, ","tha-ap332:21.4":"sayambhu aggapuggalo. ","tha-ap332:22.1":"Aho buddha aho dhamma, ","tha-ap332:22.2":"aho no satthusampada; ","tha-ap332:22.3":"Ekacchattassa danena, ","tha-ap332:22.4":"duggatim nupapajjaham. ","tha-ap332:23.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap332:23.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap332:23.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap332:23.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap332:24.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap332:24.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap332:24.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap332:25.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saparivarachattadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap332:26.1":"Saparivarachattadayakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap332:27.1":"Umapupphiyavaggo tettimsatimo. ","tha-ap332:28.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap332:29.1":"Umapupphanca pulinam, ","tha-ap332:29.2":"haso yanno nimittako; ","tha-ap332:29.3":"Samsavako niggundi ca, ","tha-ap332:29.4":"sumanam pupphachattako; ","tha-ap332:29.5":"Saparivarachatto ca, ","tha-ap332:29.6":"gatha sattasatuttarati. "}